Bocquier P(1), Collinson MA(2), Clark SJ(3), Gerritsen AA(4), Kahn K(2), TollMan 
SM(2).

Author information:
(1)Université Catholique de Louvain, Louvain-la-Neuve, Belgium ; MRC/Wits Rural 
Public Health and Health Transitions Research Unit (Agincourt), School of Public 
